{"tid":2189751,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"臺日電梯 萬元誘員工驗毒","createTime":"2020-09-05T06:11:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T06:38:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ddb89166082c59e13d8701dafc442894aa3d9686","tid":2189751,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T06:11:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200905/2WSNV2RKYZDGZHLIXTFPE5SO24/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200905%2F2WSNV2RKYZDGZHLIXTFPE5SO24%2F&d=RlZLtXxvTyjhSejQ4AJs47c9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=763aea7f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200905%2F2WSNV2RKYZDGZHLIXTFPE5SO24%2F&h=ec5f050b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200905/2WSNV2RKYZDGZHLIXTFPE5SO24/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n臺日電梯 萬元誘員工驗毒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/h2sKtPm75Ey6BUY88t4XuIE7OwU=/777x936/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BRSFTWQIQJGGBFCZNDAEULLC7Y.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fh2sKtPm75Ey6BUY88t4XuIE7OwU%3D%2F777x936%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBRSFTWQIQJGGBFCZNDAEULLC7Y.JPG&h=f0eb128c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■臺日電梯發通告，指員工如不能交出核酸檢測樣本，該員工將不會獲一萬元補貼。讀者提供相片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】特首林鄭月娥聲稱普及社區檢測計劃是「百分百自願」，不過是誤導群眾的政治口號。本報連日來接獲公私營機構員工投訴被迫參與檢測，昨日再發現一間電梯公司要求員工交出核酸檢測樣本，否則不會獲派一萬元補貼。公司高層直認不交樣本「有違政府抗疫原則」，有權不派發津貼給相關員工。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n稱無交被當「違政府抗疫原則」<br />\n<br />\n本報接獲一張由臺日電梯（香港）有限公司總經理張欽發出的通告，管方決定向今年3月起已有供強積金員工，一次性派發每人一萬元補貼，但如不能按時在昨早10時前交出核酸檢測樣本，將被視為「有違政府抗疫原則」，不會獲發相關補貼。<br />\n<br />\n記者致電該公司查詢是否有選擇性。。。。<br />\n<br />\n政府早前推出保就業計劃津貼僱主出。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，臺日電梯在政府保就業計劃中獲補貼逾116萬元，。。。。"},{"pid":"a3745a89b3e413db3ba419a68ae9119bf83d4f4f","tid":2189751,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T06:16:17.000Z","msg":"搞清楚唔係利誘 係威脅<br />\n嗰10,000係保就業抗疫基金<br />\n本應係派番比員工"},{"pid":"9f364ab8f306773f50b8cc7abac3879aecf0fe27","tid":2189751,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T06:38:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}